1
00:00:22,850 --> 00:00:29,850
♪Our tangled destiny
has trapped my heart in this life♪

2
00:00:30,020 --> 00:00:36,060
♪Will I see you again in the next life♪

3
00:00:36,550 --> 00:00:43,500
♪Keep a piece of peach blossom
to remember the past and say goodbye♪

4
00:00:43,830 --> 00:00:49,920
♪But I still miss you
with tears in my eyes♪

5
00:00:50,640 --> 00:00:57,250
♪Dig a hole, plant a tree, but the leaves
and flowers remind me of our past♪

6
00:00:57,480 --> 00:01:03,710
♪Sow the seeds of love,
but they bloom on the wrong path♪

7
00:01:04,340 --> 00:01:11,060
♪Move on, let go,
forget everything about you♪

8
00:01:11,280 --> 00:01:18,220
♪Flowers fall on the road
where I fell in love with you♪

9
00:01:32,980 --> 00:01:37,660
=Stolen Love=

10
00:01:37,860 --> 00:01:40,700
=Episode 37=

11
00:01:42,640 --> 00:01:44,440
You must know

12
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:47,520
Xiao Chuyi and I have been
rivals for many years.

13
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:49,120
Since you're his woman,

14
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:52,680
I won't let you go easily tonight.

15
00:02:05,960 --> 00:02:09,080
The jailers delivered
deer blood to me every meal.

16
00:02:09,760 --> 00:02:13,320
Someone never wanted you
to leave unscathed.

17
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:15,680
Stay back! Go away!

18
00:02:15,680 --> 00:02:16,520
Go away!

19
00:02:18,120 --> 00:02:19,080
Go away!

20
00:02:21,560 --> 00:02:22,640
Get off me!

21
00:02:29,520 --> 00:02:31,120
General, I won't stop you

22
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,440
from entering the prison camp.

23
00:02:32,880 --> 00:02:33,760
According to the rules,

24
00:02:33,960 --> 00:02:35,160
you need to be unarmed.

25
00:02:43,440 --> 00:02:45,320
The Crown Prince has said
no one can get in!

26
00:03:25,910 --> 00:03:29,700
♪Across mountains♪

27
00:03:30,100 --> 00:03:33,160
♪Sad songs echo in the air♪

28
00:03:33,870 --> 00:03:37,420
♪Talking to the moon♪

29
00:03:37,420 --> 00:03:39,980
♪It changes like my mood♪

30
00:03:41,600 --> 00:03:45,140
♪On the riverbank♪

31
00:03:45,620 --> 00:03:48,100
♪We said goodbye♪

32
00:03:48,440 --> 00:03:51,910
♪Wishing you'd come back to me♪

33
00:03:52,130 --> 00:03:54,210
♪But you never answered♪

34
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:55,200
I'm here.

35
00:03:55,990 --> 00:03:57,950
♪My cries♪

36
00:03:58,070 --> 00:03:59,690
♪And sighs♪

37
00:04:00,110 --> 00:04:02,970
♪Are buried in the snow♪

38
00:04:03,960 --> 00:04:05,670
♪Horses run♪

39
00:04:05,830 --> 00:04:07,350
♪Into my dreams♪

40
00:04:07,790 --> 00:04:11,100
♪And I see you again♪

41
00:04:11,650 --> 00:04:13,370
♪You left♪

42
00:04:13,480 --> 00:04:15,210
♪Broke my heart♪

43
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:18,840
Xiao Chuyi,

44
00:04:19,160 --> 00:04:20,640
now that you've come,

45
00:04:20,640 --> 00:04:22,360
you'll never get out of here alive!

46
00:04:22,960 --> 00:04:23,800
Watch out!

47
00:04:29,510 --> 00:04:32,520
♪I've traveled a thousand miles♪

48
00:04:32,520 --> 00:04:36,770
♪Only to keep the moon in sight♪

49
00:04:36,770 --> 00:04:40,220
♪For it once shone upon your face♪

50
00:04:41,100 --> 00:04:44,840
♪When you looked at me in the eye♪

51
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:48,090
♪I've said goodbye a thousand times♪

52
00:04:48,100 --> 00:04:52,020
♪Only to call your name again♪

53
00:04:52,200 --> 00:04:55,880
♪For it's the only thing♪

54
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:59,890
♪I'll never forget♪

55
00:05:00,360 --> 00:05:03,410
♪I've traveled a thousand miles♪

56
00:05:03,410 --> 00:05:07,720
♪Only to keep the moon in sight♪

57
00:05:07,720 --> 00:05:11,560
♪For it once shone upon your face♪

58
00:05:12,050 --> 00:05:15,760
♪When you looked at me in the eye♪

59
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:18,640
Why did you come back?

60
00:05:20,020 --> 00:05:20,940
From now on,

61
00:05:21,600 --> 00:05:23,080
I won't let you leave me again.

62
00:05:23,220 --> 00:05:26,590
♪For it's the only thing♪

63
00:05:27,090 --> 00:05:30,890
♪I'll never forget♪

64
00:05:34,850 --> 00:05:38,210
♪Till the day that I die♪

65
00:05:52,260 --> 00:05:54,230
You should be marching towards Wujiang,

66
00:05:54,920 --> 00:05:56,200
yet you came back to the capital,

67
00:05:56,320 --> 00:05:57,640
and many people have seen you.

68
00:05:58,040 --> 00:06:00,000
The Crown Prince
will definitely slander you.

69
00:06:00,160 --> 00:06:01,960
I'm going to teach him a lesson anyway.

70
00:06:02,160 --> 00:06:03,000
No.

71
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:08,160
It's my family issue.

72
00:06:08,680 --> 00:06:10,000
You're just an outsider.

73
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:13,200
I thought you'd be safe

74
00:06:13,210 --> 00:06:14,240
after I left the capital.

75
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:16,320
It turns out

76
00:06:17,420 --> 00:06:18,720
someone doesn't want me to leave.

77
00:06:18,720 --> 00:06:20,120
Then you shouldn't have come back.

78
00:06:22,520 --> 00:06:23,960
A master is like
a father to his disciples.

79
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,440
Please let me do this

80
00:06:28,440 --> 00:06:29,640
for you.

81
00:06:30,880 --> 00:06:32,400
Otherwise, I can't focus on the war.

82
00:06:38,520 --> 00:06:39,520
When you love someone,

83
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:44,200
no matter where he is and

84
00:06:45,240 --> 00:06:46,240
what he's going through,

85
00:06:47,520 --> 00:06:48,840
as long as he's not around you,

86
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:50,600
you'll never feel safe.

87
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:53,600
Chuyi.

88
00:06:54,440 --> 00:06:55,880
I also want to feel safe.

89
00:06:57,560 --> 00:06:58,960
I know I can't persuade you,

90
00:06:59,600 --> 00:07:00,440
but if

91
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:03,840
you don't want me to die with regrets,

92
00:07:05,320 --> 00:07:07,040
please go back and wait for my message.

93
00:07:07,200 --> 00:07:08,600
It's not that simple.

94
00:07:09,400 --> 00:07:10,840
I'm afraid they have another plan.

95
00:07:11,440 --> 00:07:12,800
Let's wait until

96
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:16,240
I get the cure from him tonight.

97
00:07:16,560 --> 00:07:17,400
Okay.

98
00:07:18,640 --> 00:07:19,760
I'll wait until midnight.

99
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:40,360
Lord Zhou, you foresaw everything.

100
00:07:40,770 --> 00:07:42,600
I thought Xiao Chuyi couldn't make it.

101
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,440
When I was about to kill
the Crown Prince's man

102
00:07:44,440 --> 00:07:45,400
and save Lady Lu,

103
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:47,320
he arrived.

104
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:49,880
Did he come back alone?

105
00:07:49,880 --> 00:07:51,400
Not even with his henchman.

106
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:55,120
Take the Crown Prince's token
and order

107
00:07:55,120 --> 00:07:56,680
the soldiers of Wujiang
to enter the city.

108
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,840
(Order)
Don't miss the chance.

109
00:07:57,840 --> 00:07:59,280
I'll shut down the city,

110
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:01,040
and Xiao Chuyi will never get out.

111
00:08:01,040 --> 00:08:02,440
We'll kill him

112
00:08:02,640 --> 00:08:03,560
before they're back.

113
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:04,840
How should we close the gate?

114
00:08:06,040 --> 00:08:07,400
The Crown Prince

115
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:09,840
should pay the price.

116
00:08:10,620 --> 00:08:12,300
(Zhou's Mansion)

117
00:08:12,320 --> 00:08:13,920
Che!

118
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,280
Where did you take Che?

119
00:08:19,320 --> 00:08:20,520
What do you want?

120
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:22,240
I need something from you.

121
00:08:22,640 --> 00:08:23,760
When I get it,

122
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:25,040
you'll see Che.

123
00:08:37,280 --> 00:08:40,000
If the Crown Prince knows
I took the scroll out,

124
00:08:40,320 --> 00:08:41,520
he'll stop giving me the cure.

125
00:08:41,920 --> 00:08:42,760
Yunxi,

126
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,360
I'll never hurt you

127
00:08:44,360 --> 00:08:45,520
or Che.

128
00:08:45,840 --> 00:08:47,880
I'll do what Xiao Chuyi can't do.

129
00:08:48,080 --> 00:08:48,920
I'll save Che.

130
00:09:03,120 --> 00:09:03,960
Wait for me.

131
00:09:20,800 --> 00:09:21,640
Chuyi.

132
00:09:21,880 --> 00:09:22,880
I'll escort you.

133
00:09:22,880 --> 00:09:23,800
You must leave now.

134
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:30,920
Huai County's revolt

135
00:09:30,920 --> 00:09:31,920
is not real.

136
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,080
They did it

137
00:09:33,080 --> 00:09:34,680
to lure you back to the capital

138
00:09:34,680 --> 00:09:35,960
when your army is miles away.

139
00:09:36,120 --> 00:09:37,320
Please listen to me.

140
00:09:37,470 --> 00:09:38,310
Leave now!

141
00:09:38,310 --> 00:09:39,270
If I leave,

142
00:09:39,270 --> 00:09:40,480
they'll definitely hurt Yun.

143
00:09:41,400 --> 00:09:42,240
Your Highness,

144
00:09:42,360 --> 00:09:43,400
Zhou Yanyu went to the court,

145
00:09:43,400 --> 00:09:44,920
and he was granted
a golden sword breaker.

146
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:46,880
They heard His Majesty called
the prince a nasty man

147
00:09:46,880 --> 00:09:47,720
and wanted to ruin him.

148
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,760
Here's my order.

149
00:09:52,920 --> 00:09:53,840
Find the Crown Prince.

150
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:54,680
Aye.

151
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,880
Brother, go back to your mansion.

152
00:09:56,880 --> 00:09:59,000
Don't let your people get involved.

153
00:09:59,000 --> 00:10:00,240
The prince is going to fall.

154
00:10:00,880 --> 00:10:02,280
You must stay calm at this point.

155
00:10:04,080 --> 00:10:04,920
Chuyi.

156
00:10:05,160 --> 00:10:06,040
Seven years ago,

157
00:10:06,040 --> 00:10:07,880
you posed as me
to distract their main force.

158
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:09,640
I won't abandon you this time.

159
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:10,960
If I leave now,

160
00:10:10,960 --> 00:10:12,440
I'll become a shameless deserter!

161
00:10:12,440 --> 00:10:13,280
Brother!

162
00:10:13,280 --> 00:10:14,800
You're going to take the throne.

163
00:10:14,800 --> 00:10:16,120
You can't make mistakes.

164
00:10:16,120 --> 00:10:17,680
If anything happens,

165
00:10:17,680 --> 00:10:19,600
all our efforts will be in vain.

166
00:10:19,600 --> 00:10:21,360
Who will avenge the brothers

167
00:10:21,360 --> 00:10:22,600
died in Luoxia Ridge?

168
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:24,870
Chuyi...

169
00:10:24,870 --> 00:10:25,720
- Guards!
- Aye!

170
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:26,570
- Take him back!
- Aye!

171
00:10:26,580 --> 00:10:27,600
No. Chuyi!

172
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:42,800
Zhou Yanyu!

173
00:10:42,800 --> 00:10:43,840
Are you going to rebel?

174
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:47,200
I've given the scroll to His Majesty.

175
00:10:49,000 --> 00:10:50,640
You're the traitor now.

176
00:10:50,920 --> 00:10:52,320
His Majesty granted me

177
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,600
the golden sword breaker.

178
00:10:53,760 --> 00:10:54,760
It'll knock the evil ruler

179
00:10:54,760 --> 00:10:56,160
and nasty officials.

180
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:57,680
If the Crown Prince surrenders,

181
00:10:57,680 --> 00:10:59,040
he shall meet His Highness.

182
00:11:00,040 --> 00:11:01,600
If he resists,

183
00:11:01,920 --> 00:11:02,960
I'll lead the forbidden guards

184
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:04,040
to kill the traitor.

185
00:11:04,440 --> 00:11:05,280
What?

186
00:11:06,350 --> 00:11:07,200
Nasty dog!

187
00:11:07,200 --> 00:11:08,320
You're my shadow guard!

188
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,440
Kill him now!

189
00:11:14,360 --> 00:11:15,780
I forgot to tell you.

190
00:11:17,680 --> 00:11:19,720
This is Prince Luesha from Wujiang.

191
00:11:19,920 --> 00:11:20,760
Your Highness.

192
00:11:23,880 --> 00:11:25,480
We are the ones who helped you

193
00:11:25,760 --> 00:11:27,040
form an alliance with Wujiang.

194
00:11:32,160 --> 00:11:34,040
It turns out you're the mastermind.

195
00:11:35,400 --> 00:11:36,680
A clean hand wants no washing.

196
00:11:37,360 --> 00:11:38,800
If you didn't want
to betray the country,

197
00:11:38,800 --> 00:11:41,000
how could I have tempted you?

198
00:11:43,040 --> 00:11:44,080
I need to see Father.

199
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:45,120
I need to see Father!

200
00:11:45,120 --> 00:11:46,120
I need to see Father!

201
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:46,960
I need...

202
