We're at war,

208
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:51,680
and you risked your life to come.

209
00:12:52,040 --> 00:12:53,080
What do you want?

210
00:12:53,080 --> 00:12:55,440
Prince Su took his best soldiers
to attack Luoxia Ridge,

211
00:12:55,800 --> 00:12:57,720
and you kept losing.

212
00:12:58,110 --> 00:13:00,320
The border of Wujiang will soon fall,

213
00:13:00,410 --> 00:13:01,280
and

214
00:13:01,280 --> 00:13:04,320
Tianyun's army will break in
through Luoxia Ridge.

215
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:07,320
My father and I are ready to die.

216
00:13:07,320 --> 00:13:08,490
What if

217
00:13:08,490 --> 00:13:10,200
you can get Prince Su's Defense Map?

218
00:13:13,120 --> 00:13:14,120
If we have it,

219
00:13:14,680 --> 00:13:17,000
Father can not only defend Luoxia Ridge

220
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:19,120
but eliminate all of them.

221
00:13:19,320 --> 00:13:20,160
Recently,

222
00:13:20,680 --> 00:13:21,840
our Crown Prince

223
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:24,760
ordered my mother to
discuss with your father about alliance.

224
00:13:25,080 --> 00:13:26,040
And you can

225
00:13:26,040 --> 00:13:28,080
ask for this thing at the meeting.

226
00:13:28,720 --> 00:13:30,960
The Zhous have served three emperors,

227
00:13:32,120 --> 00:13:33,920
and you're the top scholar

228
00:13:33,920 --> 00:13:35,280
who works for Hanlin Academy.

229
00:13:35,280 --> 00:13:37,120
You have a bright future.

230
00:13:37,240 --> 00:13:38,800
Why would you help me?

231
00:13:39,820 --> 00:13:43,320
My cousin Xiao Chuyi
is Prince Su's soldier.

232
00:13:44,880 --> 00:13:46,240
I want him to die.

