♪Broke my heart♪

241
00:14:25,240 --> 00:14:29,120
♪Wish you could hold me in your arms♪

242
00:14:29,720 --> 00:14:31,960
♪Even your name♪

243
00:14:32,160 --> 00:14:36,440
♪Is a forbidden word♪

